title: Is a Manual Transmission Swap Worth It?
author: Donut Media
description:
Thanks to Ebay Motors for sponsoring this video! CLICK here https://ebayvehicle.com/app/Donut to search through thousands of cars and parts & list those project cars and spare parts sitting around!

So far we’ve beat the absolute crap out of our new e36 BUT the automatic transmission is kinda ruining the party for us. So today we are turning our family automatic sedan into... well still a family sedan with a cooler shift stick. Was it all worth it???
